{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"ca7fa345b0","title":"毛远新传达周恩来对哈尔滨军事工程学院的指示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"82aff53899","index":0,"year":1967,"month":12,"day":3,"articleId":"ca7fa345b0","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"大联合","id":"18bf6a78fe","type":"主题"},{"name":"指示","id":"2d13338754","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"周恩来","id":"523bb79e8f","type":"人物"},{"name":"周总理","id":"838b5f2c9d","type":"人物"},{"name":"关键人物文稿","id":"c20d333791","type":"文稿大类"},{"name":"造反运动和派别斗争","id":"d48f0ea3e8","type":"主题"},{"name":"毛远新","id":"f8d6ecb146","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第一版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"b7ad58134e","name":"毛远新"}]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"ca5bab91e1","type":"title","text":"毛远新传达周恩来对哈尔滨军事工程学院的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"ca7fa345b0","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3065bbeb73","type":"paragraph","text":"12月4日下午两点，毛远新同志来西苑旅社，找边世军等军工同志传达了3日晚周总理关于军工大联合问题的指示。基本精神是：","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"ca7fa345b0","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9bce32a622","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席、党中央、周总理非常关心哈军工问题，要求军工两派尽快实现革命大联合，以团结对敌；要做榜样，立新功。军工两派的联合，将促进黑龙江问题的解决和东北三省的革命大联合，同时，对反帝反修具有重大意义。中央决定，军工两派的联合问题在北京解决要求双方达成协议，希望双方协商的基本内容是：","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"ca7fa345b0","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ece6cbb134","type":"paragraph","text":"（1）各级权力机构群众团体代表对等，结合干部由双方协商决定；","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"ca7fa345b0","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"874df539b7","type":"paragraph","text":"（2）双方立即停止相互攻击的宣传活动；","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"ca7fa345b0","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f7b652c782","type":"paragraph","text":"（3）以此为榜样，向全省全市发出大联合的呼吁，等等。","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"ca7fa345b0","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"30bcddb178","type":"paragraph","text":"同时，哈一机的问题中央也决定在京解决。","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"ca7fa345b0","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}